channel.title: Blackocean x HAYVN - where are you now
channel.description: https://soundcloud.com/blckocean/blackocean-x-hayvn-where-are-you-now enjoy this ember island inspired cover of Jack U's "Where Are You Now" (feat. Justin Beiber). I used Auxy to make the instrumental, and added extra samples and did mixing and mastering in FL Studio. Loved working with @HAYVN on this! Hope you all enjoy!
